{"tid":549701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一年一度，支那童搶小一學位開始喇！","createTime":"2018-02-04T02:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T09:33:28.000Z","uid":29314,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4cbafb91da8b071e0776b7a0f7c8cac9b9731f28","tid":549701,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T02:13:26.000Z","msg":"上星期中國國家領導人，廣東省政協「周星馳」叫香港青年北上發展；言猶在耳，呢頭就見到成堆雙非童走黎香港，搶小一學位。<br />\n<br />\n我就真係唔明，既然香港都係靠中國打救、既然中國機遇處處，發展欣欣向榮，既然普通話先係未來全球通用既語言，既然又大灣區又一帶一路又十三五規劃又大珠三角講到無得輸咁款&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n班雙非童既父母好應該近水樓台先得月，留返係中國國內培育下一代先至係。點解要捨近取遠，不惜使成千萬都要走黎香港，同香港人既細路爭小一學位呢？<br />\n<br />\n學毛澤東話齋：「群眾的眼睛是雪亮的！」香港班高官同權貴喊破喉嚨，日叫夜叫香港年青人離開香港去中國發展都無用。我就只信毛澤東！你呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/101234_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F101234_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e1202319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西米Go fb &amp; ig同步連載：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWestRiceGoo&d=BAvQ12%2F47ujByeBCDDnyswRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d93a4078\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwestricegoo&d=BAvQ12%2F47ujByeBCDDnyswRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=0c214966\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo</a>"},{"pid":"6fdf2cafbb3f6ccba011beaba71a1ec6d82d20da","tid":549701,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718e61b71ccd0387859dd89610f9e1b5c8f90688","tid":549701,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:38:16.000Z"