ke":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:51:58.000Z","msg":"過千萬買樓，交成幾球稅，呢D貢獻幾多香港人一生都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e584faa7f99281269eb680aa7c9efe84fa0e1a88","tid":549701,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0074bcf6f277259c129c613912eaf3774ac2610d","tid":549701,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d82a1547aea4315df4bae8c84860c4e91d79ab6","tid":549701,"uid":45353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4c3fbc1069adf6a4df807ae0ee0fafede7be7fa","tid":549701,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:41:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"睇少d電視啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:45:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:53:13.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦扯到去世襲權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何況兩代香港土生土長講屌你老母玩比卡超大<br />\n香港人世襲有咩問題"},{"pid":"4ca8acc27916289cc755efa6bdcce36e38d0438f","tid":549701,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:53:34.000Z","msg":"仲有，香港也是中國的一部分，如果你係港獨狗，咁香港其實跟你毫無關係。"},{"pid":"820ebf1623caffc668eaca755f3dfd2d16a4b600","tid":549701,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31b5ae1887c0147e14bb781dfcded60f4f2267f","tid":549701,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e584faa7f99281269eb680aa7c9efe84fa0e1a88","tid":549701,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0074bcf6f277259c129c613912eaf3774ac2610d","tid":549701,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d82a1547aea4315df4bae8c84860c4e91d79ab6","tid":549701,"uid":45353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB